The next [United Nations Climate Change Conference (COP 16)
](http://cc2010.mx/en/)will take place from November 29 until December 10,
2010 in[ Cancun](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Canc%C3%BAn), Mexico.

There are several discussions on the subject. Bloggers are analyzing whether
the conference will bring the usual disappointment about a lack of action from
the climate change and ecological actors, or if this time it will provide a
new perspective and a new opportunity where failure is not an option _._

